TITLE: Checking for Writable File System in VSCode Extensions
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of the new fs.isWritableFileSystem API in VSCode that allows extensions to check if a given file system supports writing operations. This is particularly useful for custom editors to determine if they should show a readonly UI.
