SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/vscode-docs/blob/main/remote-release-notes/v1_63.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
"remote.SSH.serverPickPortsFromRange": {\n    "work-main": "60000-61000",\n    "work-test": "60000-61000",\n    "localhost": "5000-6000"\n}
```

