LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
{}{}{}{}{}{}{}{}... O(N / log N) many
{
    {}{}{}{}{}{}{}{}... O(N / log N) many
    {
        ... O(log N) many nested bracket pairs
            {
                {}{}{}{}{}{}{}{}... O(N / log N) many
                {} [1]
            }
        ...
    }
}
```

