TITLE: Changing ExtensionTerminalOptions-based Terminal Names in VS Code
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to dynamically change the name of terminals created with ExtensionTerminalOptions using the Pseudoterminal.onDidChangeName event in a VS Code extension.
