TITLE: Writing a Hello World Program - C++ Application - cpp
DESCRIPTION: This C++ snippet provides a complete Hello World application using vectors and string streams. It demonstrates core features like vector initialization, iteration, and output using 'cout'. Dependencies are the C++ standard library with support for <iostream>, <vector>, and <string>. Inputs are none; the output prints each message word separated by spaces. Intended for use in the created 'helloworld.cpp' file.
